---
// DemoWidget — live Datagma phone/email finder demo
// 4 search modes: LinkedIn URL | Name + Company | Name + Domain | Name + Email
// Rate limited: 3 phones/IP/24h (masked) + 3 emails/IP/24h (full)
---

<section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">

  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/3 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-blue-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-25"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-sky-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <div class="text-center mb-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 text-green-700 text-xs font-bold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
        Live demo — no account needed
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-gray-900 mb-3 tracking-tight">
        Try it yourself — find a direct mobile
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">
        3 phone searches included, no credit card. Phones shown partially masked — register to see full numbers.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-200/80 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(37,99,235,.1),0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,.06)]">

      <!-- Decorative gradient -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-sky-400 to-blue-600"></div>

      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">

        <!-- Mode tabs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-1.5">
          {[
            { id: "linkedin",    label: "LinkedIn URL",        icon: "fab fa-linkedin" },
            { id: "nameCompany", label: "Name + Company",      icon: "fas fa-building" },
            { id: "nameDomain",  label: "Name + Domain",       icon: "fas fa-globe" },
            { id: "nameEmail",   label: "Name + Email",        icon: "fas fa-envelope" },
          ].map((tab) => (
            <button
              class="demo-tab flex-1 min-w-[120px] flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-3 py-2.5 rounded-xl text-xs font-bold transition-all"
              data-mode={tab.id}
            >
              <i class={`${tab.icon} text-[11px]`}></i>
              {tab.label}
            </button>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Form inputs -->
        <form id="demo-form" class="space-y-3">

          <!-- LinkedIn mode -->
          <div class="demo-inputs" data-for="linkedin">
            <input type="url" name="linkedin" placeholder="https://linkedin.com/in/firstname-lastname"
              class="demo-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-sm font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-transparent bg-white placeholder-gray-400 transition-all" />
          </div>

          <!-- Name + Company mode -->
          <div class="demo-inputs hidden" data-for="nameCompany">
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <input type="text" name="fullName" placeholder="Full name (e.g. John Smith)"
                class="demo-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-sm font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-transparent bg-white placeholder-gray-400" />
              <input type="text" name="companyName" placeholder="Company name (e.g. Stripe)"
                class="demo-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-sm font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-transparent bg-white placeholder-gray-400" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Name + Domain mode -->
          <div class="demo-inputs hidden" data-for="nameDomain">
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <input type="text" name="fullName2" placeholder="Full name (e.g. John Smith)"
                class="demo-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-sm font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-transparent bg-white placeholder-gray-400" />
              <input type="text" name="domain" placeholder="Domain (e.g. stripe.com)"
                class="demo-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-sm font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-transparent bg-white placeholder-gray-400" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Name + Email mode -->
          <div class="demo-inputs hidden" data-for="nameEmail">
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
              <input type="text" name="fullName3" placeholder="Full name (e.g. John Smith)"
                class="demo-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-sm font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-transparent bg-white placeholder-gray-400" />
              <input type="email" name="emailInput" placeholder="Work email (e.g. john@stripe.com)"
                class="demo-input w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 text-sm font-medium focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-400 focus:border-transparent bg-white placeholder-gray-400" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <button id="demo-submit" type="submit"
            class="w-full bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3.5 px-6 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-md shadow-blue-200 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm">
            <i class="fas fa-search text-xs"></i>
            <span id="demo-btn-text">Find direct mobile</span>
          </button>

        </form>

        <!-- Credits bar -->
        <div id="demo-credits" class="mt-4 flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] text-gray-400 font-semibold">
          <span id="credits-phones"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt mr-1 text-blue-400"></i><span id="phones-remaining">3</span> phone searches left today</span>
          <span id="credits-emails"><i class="fas fa-envelope mr-1 text-violet-400"></i><span id="emails-remaining">3</span> email searches left today</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Error message -->
        <div id="demo-error" class="hidden mt-4 p-4 bg-red-50 border border-red-200 rounded-2xl text-sm text-red-700 font-medium flex items-center gap-2">
          <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle text-red-400"></i>
          <span id="demo-error-msg">An error occurred. Please try again.</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Results -->
        <div id="demo-result" class="hidden mt-6">

          <!-- Loading skeleton (shown while fetching) -->
          <div id="demo-loading" class="hidden space-y-3 animate-pulse">
            <div class="h-4 bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-1/2"></div>
            <div class="h-3 bg-gray-100 rounded-full w-1/3"></div>
            <div class="h-8 bg-gray-100 rounded-2xl w-full"></div>
          </div>

          <!-- Result card -->
          <div id="demo-card" class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50/50 overflow-hidden">

            <!-- Contact header -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-5 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
              <div id="result-avatar" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-sky-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-extrabold text-sm shrink-0 shadow-sm">?</div>
              <div class="min-w-0">
                <div id="result-name" class="font-display font-bold text-gray-900 text-base leading-tight"></div>
                <div id="result-role" class="text-gray-500 text-xs mt-0.5 truncate"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-auto shrink-0">
                <span class="text-[10px] font-extrabold text-green-700 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">
                  <i class="fas fa-check-circle mr-1"></i>Found
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Contact details -->
            <div class="p-5 space-y-3">

              <!-- Phone -->
              <div id="phone-row" class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt text-blue-600 text-sm"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">Direct mobile</div>
                  <div id="phone-value" class="font-display font-extrabold text-xl text-gray-900 tracking-wide font-mono"></div>
                </div>
                <div id="whatsapp-badge" class="hidden shrink-0">
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-green-700 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">
                    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp text-[11px]"></i>WhatsApp
                  </span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phone limit reached -->
              <div id="phone-limit" class="hidden flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-xl">
                <i class="fas fa-lock text-amber-500 shrink-0"></i>
                <div class="min-w-0">
                  <div class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-800">Phone limit reached for today</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">Create a free account to get more searches. 3 phones included every month.</div>
                </div>
                <a href="https://app.datagma.com/register" class="shrink-0 bg-blue-600 text-white text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">
                  Register free
                </a>
              </div>

              <!-- No phone found -->
              <div id="phone-none" class="hidden flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
                <i class="fas fa-phone-slash text-gray-400 shrink-0 text-sm"></i>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">No direct mobile found for this contact. <a href="https://app.datagma.com/register" class="text-blue-600 font-bold hover:underline">Try another search →</a></div>
              </div>

              <!-- Email -->
              <div id="email-row" class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-violet-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <i class="fas fa-envelope text-violet-600 text-sm"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="min-w-0 flex-1">
                  <div class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-0.5">Professional email</div>
                  <div id="email-value" class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-800 font-semibold truncate"></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Email limit reached -->
              <div id="email-limit" class="hidden flex items-center gap-3 p-3 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope text-gray-300 shrink-0"></i>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Email limit reached. <a href="https://app.datagma.com/register" class="text-blue-600 font-bold hover:underline">Register free to continue →</a></div>
              </div>

            </div>

            <!-- CTA footer -->
            <div class="px-5 py-4 bg-blue-50/50 border-t border-blue-100 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3">
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 font-semibold">
                <i class="fas fa-lock mr-1 text-blue-400"></i>Register free to see full numbers & get 3 phones/month
              </div>
              <a href="https://app.datagma.com/register"
                class="shrink-0 bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-xl text-xs hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors shadow-md shadow-blue-200">
                Create free account →
              </a>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
(function () {
  var TOKEN_URL  = "/api/demo-token";
  var ENRICH_URL = "/api/demo-enrich";
  var currentMode = "linkedin";
  var cachedToken = null;
  var tokenExpiry = 0;

  // ── Tab switching ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  var tabs = document.querySelectorAll(".demo-tab");
  var inputGroups = document.querySelectorAll(".demo-inputs");

  function setActiveTab(mode) {
    currentMode = mode;
    tabs.forEach(function (t) {
      var active = t.dataset.mode === mode;
      t.className = t.className.replace(/bg-\S+|text-\S+|shadow-\S+/g, "").trim();
      if (active) {
        t.classList.add("bg-white", "text-blue-600", "shadow-sm");
      } else {
        t.classList.add("text-gray-500", "hover:text-gray-700");
      }
    });
    inputGroups.forEach(function (g) {
      g.classList.toggle("hidden", g.dataset.for !== mode);
    });
    hideResult();
    hideError();
  }

  tabs.forEach(function (t) {
    t.addEventListener("click", function () { setActiveTab(t.dataset.mode); });
  });
  setActiveTab("linkedin");

  // ── Token fetch (cached, refreshed before expiry) ───────────────────────────
  async function getToken() {
    if (cachedToken && Date.now() < tokenExpiry - 5000) return cachedToken;
    try {
      var r = await fetch(TOKEN_URL);
      if (!r.ok) throw new Error("token_error");
      var d = await r.json();
      cachedToken = d.token;
      tokenExpiry = Date.now() + (d.expiresIn || 300) * 1000;
      return cachedToken;
    } catch {
      return null;
    }
  }

  // ── UI helpers ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  var btnText = document.getElementById("demo-btn-text");
  var submitBtn = document.getElementById("demo-submit");
  var resultEl = document.getElementById("demo-result");
  var errorEl  = document.getElementById("demo-error");
  var errorMsg = document.getElementById("demo-error-msg");

  function setLoading(on) {
    submitBtn.disabled = on;
    btnText.textContent = on ? "Searching…" : "Find direct mobile";
    submitBtn.classList.toggle("opacity-60", on);
    submitBtn.classList.toggle("cursor-not-allowed", on);
  }

  function showError(msg) {
    errorEl.classList.remove("hidden");
    errorMsg.textContent = msg;
    resultEl.classList.add("hidden");
  }

  function hideError() { errorEl.classList.add("hidden"); }
  function hideResult() { resultEl.classList.add("hidden"); }

  function updateCredits(credits) {
    if (!credits) return;
    var pr = document.getElementById("phones-remaining");
    var er = document.getElementById("emails-remaining");
    if (pr) pr.textContent = credits.phonesRemaining;
    if (er) er.textContent = credits.emailsRemaining;
  }

  // ── Display result ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  function showResult(data) {
    if (!data.found && !data.phone && !data.email) {
      showError("No contact found for this search. Try a LinkedIn URL or double-check the inputs.");
      return;
    }

    resultEl.classList.remove("hidden");
    hideError();

    var contact = data.contact || {};
    var name = contact.fullName || "—";
    var initials = name.split(" ").map(function (p) { return p[0]; }).join("").slice(0, 2).toUpperCase() || "?";
    var role = [contact.jobTitle, contact.company].filter(Boolean).join(" · ");

    document.getElementById("result-avatar").textContent = initials;
    document.getElementById("result-name").textContent   = name;
    document.getElementById("result-role").textContent   = role;

    // Phone
    var phoneRow   = document.getElementById("phone-row");
    var phoneLimit = document.getElementById("phone-limit");
    var phoneNone  = document.getElementById("phone-none");
    var phoneVal   = document.getElementById("phone-value");
    var waBadge    = document.getElementById("whatsapp-badge");

    phoneRow.classList.add("hidden");
    phoneLimit.classList.add("hidden");
    phoneNone.classList.add("hidden");

    if (data.phone) {
      phoneRow.classList.remove("hidden");
      phoneVal.textContent = data.phone.masked;
      if (data.phone.whatsapp) {
        waBadge.classList.remove("hidden");
      } else {
        waBadge.classList.add("hidden");
      }
    } else if (data.phoneLimitReached) {
      phoneLimit.classList.remove("hidden");
    } else {
      phoneNone.classList.remove("hidden");
    }

    // Email
    var emailRow   = document.getElementById("email-row");
    var emailLimit = document.getElementById("email-limit");
    var emailVal   = document.getElementById("email-value");

    emailRow.classList.add("hidden");
    emailLimit.classList.add("hidden");

    if (data.email) {
      emailRow.classList.remove("hidden");
      emailVal.textContent = data.email;
    } else if (data.emailLimitReached) {
      emailLimit.classList.remove("hidden");
    }

    // Credits
    updateCredits(data.credits);
  }

  // ── Form submit ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  var form = document.getElementById("demo-form");
  form.addEventListener("submit", async function (e) {
    e.preventDefault();
    hideError();
    setLoading(true);

    var token = await getToken();
    if (!token) {
      showError("Could not initialize demo. Please refresh the page.");
      setLoading(false);
      return;
    }

    var params = new URLSearchParams({ t: token, mode: currentMode });

    if (currentMode === "linkedin") {
      var li = form.querySelector("[name=linkedin]").value.trim();
      if (!li) { showError("Please enter a LinkedIn URL."); setLoading(false); return; }
      params.set("linkedin", li);
    } else if (currentMode === "nameCompany") {
      var fn = form.querySelector("[name=fullName]").value.trim();
      var cn = form.querySelector("[name=companyName]").value.trim();
      if (!fn || !cn) { showError("Please enter both full name and company name."); setLoading(false); return; }
      params.set("fullName", fn);
      params.set("companyName", cn);
    } else if (currentMode === "nameDomain") {
      var fn2 = form.querySelector("[name=fullName2]").value.trim();
      var dom = form.querySelector("[name=domain]").value.trim();
      if (!fn2 || !dom) { showError("Please enter both full name and domain."); setLoading(false); return; }
      params.set("fullName", fn2);
      params.set("domain", dom);
    } else if (currentMode === "nameEmail") {
      var fn3 = form.querySelector("[name=fullName3]").value.trim();
      var em  = form.querySelector("[name=emailInput]").value.trim();
      if (!fn3 || !em) { showError("Please enter both full name and email."); setLoading(false); return; }
      params.set("fullName", fn3);
      params.set("email", em);
    }

    try {
      var resp = await fetch(ENRICH_URL + "?" + params.toString());
      var json = await resp.json();

      if (resp.status === 429) {
        showError("Daily search limit reached. Create a free account to continue.");
      } else if (resp.status === 401) {
        cachedToken = null;
        showError("Session expired. Please try again.");
      } else if (resp.status === 404 || (json && !json.found)) {
        showResult({ found: false });
      } else if (!resp.ok) {
        showError(json.error === "api_unreachable" ? "Datagma API is temporarily unavailable." : "Search failed. Please try again.");
      } else {
        showResult(json);
      }
    } catch {
      showError("Network error. Please check your connection and try again.");
    }

    setLoading(false);
  });

  // Prefetch token on load
  getToken();
})();
</script>

<style>
.demo-tab { cursor: pointer; }
#phone-value { letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
</style>
